mscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">paper</a> and <a href=3D"https://lin=
k.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23656910.289653/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbHNibHVlc2t5=
